desc:RepeatClipper
author: tdihp
version: 0.1
about:
  This fx takes the idea of clipper to a different direction, instead of keeping
  a flat line, this fx repeat or mirror the signal back to its dynamic range,
  making unpleasant distortive waveform out of the original as soon as it
  crosses threshold.

